{"tid":2258293,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"三國志文化展2020","createTime":"2020-10-26T02:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T02:32:11.000Z","uid":188773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3abe31c24344a703d0e69c49ff5283b127bbbecc","tid":2258293,"uid":188773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:32:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">三國志文化展2020<br />\n大約1800年前，以東漢王朝的混亂為發端的三國時代，隨着眾多武將的榮枯盛衰被記錄下來，成為帶有歷史性的傳說而普及。因此，又產生了詩文和繪畫，還有像關羽那樣集尊崇於一身的「神化式」武將&mdash;&mdash;這些便成為了如今豐富多彩的「三國志文化」。<br />\n<br />\n三國志文化展2020之強漢傾頹<br />\n<a href=\"http://travelbyod.blogspot.com/2020/10/sanguo-exhibition-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravelbyod.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F10%2Fsanguo-exhibition-1.html&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=7bc8cd36\" target=\"_blank\">http://travelbyod.blogspot.com/2020/10/sanguo-exhibition-1.html</a></span>"}]}